Being alone and walking alone and thinking about yourself always makes you feel better. It makes you feel better when you're not feeling well and you're tired and you're confused about what you want. So being alone is absolutely adorable.
But sometimes you need someone around yourself to inspire you to be happier and be the only one who can make impossible things possible.
So if you don't have kind of this people around yourself just wait for it...
One day you will be able to fell in real love.
One day you will be the person who you wanted to be.
Actually your thoughts and your actions do this....
Believe yourself and believe your life. Believe that your life is the most important thing.
Just don't get distracted with others speaks. Don't get disappointed with every single breakage that you have.
Anyway be optimistic and pleasure your lifetime.
Cause lots of good things are waiting for you ‚ù§.

One day someone told me it's not important what others are saying about you...
The fact is that others say the things that they like and they don't care about you anymore...
So, just don't listen to them. Don't care about them. Don't care about the people who makes you feel pessimistic and disappointed.
Just follow your heart and make sure that you will be able to do any impossible things. Don't try to convince them with your abilities.
You will face lots of problems just don't give up. Just keep your strength and your power and let your heart fly as a bird...
Me: lots of people has broken my heart and hurt me with their words.
But i did not quit because my dreams and my goals are the most important things in my life....
